		<h1 id="headline" itemprop="url headline name">The Man Making Silicon Valley Go Crazy for Hardware</h1>
<link itemprop="url" href="http://www.wired.com/2014/06/pch-the-company-quietly-powering-a-boom-in-hardware-startups/" />
<link itemprop="image" href="http://www.wired.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/pch-feat.jpg" />

<ul class="entry-header">
	
	<li class="author">By&nbsp;Bill Wasik&nbsp;&nbsp;</li>

	<li class="entryDate"><time itemprop="datePublished" datetime="2014-06-27T06:30:12+00:00">06.27.14</time>&nbsp;&nbsp;&#124;&nbsp;&nbsp;</li>
	<li class="entryTime">6:30 am&nbsp;&nbsp;&#124;&nbsp;&nbsp;</li>

		<li><a href="http://www.wired.com/2014/06/pch-the-company-quietly-powering-a-boom-in-hardware-startups/" rel="bookmark" title="The Man Making Silicon Valley Go Crazy for Hardware">Permalink</a></li></ul> <!-- /#authors entry-header  -->


